subject: Basketball
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: Kris Humphries and Carlos Delfino each scored 17 points and Joey Graham added 13 as the Toronto Raptors shrugged off injuries to three top players to beat the visiting Charlotte Bobcats, 98-79, Monday night.
